### Run only this parameter file is FARGO3D was build using the setup 'mhdrotor'
SetUp			mhdrotor

### Mesh parameters

Nx			1
Ny                	512
Nz			512
Ymin			0.0
Ymax			1.0
Zmin			0.0
Zmax			1.0

PeriodicY		yes
PeriodicZ		yes

Gamma			1.4
p			1.0
v0			2.0

###Setup Parameters

r1			0.1
r2			0.115

### Output control parameters
Ntot			200		Total number of time steps
Ninterm	 		1		Time steps between outputs
DT			0.001		
OutputDir		@outputs/mhdrotor

field			gasdens